ttp_template:
<group name="byte_count_dest_addr_interface_last_transition">
  Destination address: 1{{PACKETS | ORPHRASE}}.{{BYTE_COUNT | re("\\d+")}}.0.2
  Destination address: {{DEST_ADDR | ORPHRASE}}
  Tunnel-type: {{TUNNEL_TYPE | ORPHRASE}}
  State: {{STATE | ORPHRASE}}
  Last transition: {{LAST_TRANSITION | ORPHRASE}}
  Interface: {{INTERFACE | ORPHRASE}}
</group>

textfsm_template:
Value DEST_ADDR (\S+)
Value TUNNEL_TYPE (\S+)
Value STATE (Up|Down)
Value PACKETS (\d+)
Value BYTE_COUNT (\d+)
Value LAST_TRANSITION (\S+)
Value INTERFACE (\S+)

Start
  ^\s*Destination\s+address:\s+${DEST_ADDR}\s*$$
  ^\s*Tunnel-type:\s+${TUNNEL_TYPE}\s*$$
  ^\s*State:\s+${STATE}\s*$$
  ^\s*Packets:\s+${PACKETS}\s*$$
  ^\s*Byte-count:\s+${BYTE_COUNT}\s*$$
  ^\s*Last\s+transition:\s+${LAST_TRANSITION}\s*$$
  ^\s*Interface:\s+${INTERFACE}\s*$$ -> Record
